long_description    fzy is faster and shows better results than other \
                    fuzzy finders.

checksums           rmd160  9ddc7b43d1900212e7ceeecffa12442ef6d50e5a \
                    sha256  182104994d9bf1801cca100b1af56486e34a213022da315c38d5e2c342d70dbc

